# The "Find Your Lawmakers" feature requires no API keys.
# It uses the Census Bureau Geocoder (free, no auth) and the
# unitedstates/congress-legislators open dataset (free, no auth).
#
# No .env configuration is needed for this feature to work.

# Google Civic Information API key (deprecated — no longer in use)
# VITE_GOOGLE_CIVIC_API_KEY=your_google_civic_api_key_here
